data.description: The perfect home in Daphne is waiting for you! All brick, over 2100 square feet, built in 2019, has an open and desirable four bedroom two bath, traditional floorplan.  Owner has just installed new high quality luxury vinyl plank flooring in living room, dining room, hallway, and eat in kitchen area.  Only carpet is in the bedrooms.  Upon entering there is an office (could be a 5th bedroom) that can be closed off for privacy, and a formal dining room off the foyer.  The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a breakfast nook and bar.  The split floor plan has a primary bedroom with tray ceilings, crown molding and an en-suite bath with dual vanities, oversize shower, soaking tub, and dual closets. There are three secondary bedrooms, and a full bath with a tub/shower combo. The truly southern front porch is great for sipping tea and the back porch with extended deck and cover will WOW you.  Especially when you see the creek and forest view, providing nature's beauty and loads of privacy.  Custom deck has lots of room for entertaining, grilling and fun.  Property also features a gated parking pad off side of house.  All measurements taken from builders plans, buyer to verify all information deemed pertinent during their due diligence.
